{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"悼念曹荻秋同志逝世十周年","authors":["范征夫"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":3,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"范征夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变革高潮夕，承膺重任时，(1)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运筹谋治理，主政守章规。(2)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肝胆如明镜，胸怀全局棋，(3)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谦恭有美德，长者亦良师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颠倒人妖日，坚贞誓不移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侃侃排毁誉，凛凛显威仪。(4)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜难眠苦，朦胧溘逝悲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音容遗范在，海上树丰碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“变革”指“三大改造”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“主政守章规”指曹主持市政府工作期间，模范地遵守党章、宪法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“肝胆如明镜”指曹团结非党副市长，肝胆照人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“侃侃排毁誉”指曹据理驳斥“四人帮”一伙对他的诬蔑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八六年三月二十二日"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}